data.value: Which Locale is this happening in (US/UK/Canada)? Which environments is this happening in (Live/Prod2/Pre)? Which Markets or Customers does this error affect? How often? The common criteria? The overall company impact? List examples and the exact steps used to duplicate the issue. This should be accompanied by screenshots attached to the issue. Make sure you include the Customer Number and Loan Number. NOTE: If issue is regarding a single customer account, can you duplicate with another similar customer account? (i.e., Does this affect only one customer? If so, this not a Dev issue.) Version of Curo? Does the change/ request/ fix need to be approved by another department? ie. Legal, Ops, Collections.
